3127 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3128 
3129 int DocInternal::parse(int level)
3130 {
3131  int retval=RetVal_OK;
3132  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3133  DBG(("DocInternal::parse() start\n"));
3134 
3135  // first parse any number of paragraphs
3136  bool isFirst=TRUE;
3137  DocPara *lastPar=0;
3138  do
3139  {
3140  DocPara *par = new DocPara(this);
3141  if (isFirst) { par->markFirst(); isFirst=FALSE; }
3142  retval=par->parse();
3143  if (!par->isEmpty())
3144  {
3145  m_children.append(par);
3146  lastPar=par;
3147  }
3148  else
3149  {
3150  delete par;
3151  }
3152  if (retval==TK_LISTITEM)
3153  {
3154  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Invalid list item found",doctokenizerYYlineno);
3155  }
3156  } while (retval!=0 &&
3157  retval!=RetVal_Section &&
3158  retval!=RetVal_Subsection &&
3159  retval!=RetVal_Subsubsection &&
3160  retval!=RetVal_Paragraph &&
3161  retval!=RetVal_EndInternal
3162  );
3163  if (lastPar) lastPar->markLast();
3164 
3165  // then parse any number of level-n sections
3166  while ((level==1 && retval==RetVal_Section) ||
3167  (level==2 && retval==RetVal_Subsection) ||
3168  (level==3 && retval==RetVal_Subsubsection) ||
3169  (level==4 && retval==RetVal_Paragraph)
3170  )
3171  {
3172  DocSection *s=new DocSection(this,
3173  QMIN(level+Doxygen::subpageNestingLevel,5),g_token->sectionId);
3174  m_children.append(s);
3175  retval = s->parse();
3176  }
3177 
3178  if (retval==RetVal_Internal)
3179  {
3180  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"\\internal command found inside internal section");
3181  }
3182 
3183  DBG(("DocInternal::parse() end: retval=%x\n",retval));
3184  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3185  ASSERT(n==this);
3186  return retval;
3187 }

3190 
3191 int DocIndexEntry::parse()
3192 {
3193  int retval=RetVal_OK;
3194  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3195  DBG(("DocIndexEntry::parse() start\n"));
3196  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3197  if (tok!=TK_WHITESPACE)
3198  {
3199  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected whitespace after \\addindex command");
3200  goto endindexentry;
3201  }
3202  doctokenizerYYsetStateTitle();
3203  m_entry="";
3204  while ((tok=doctokenizerYYlex()))
3205  {
3206  switch (tok)
3207  {
3208  case TK_WHITESPACE:
3209  m_entry+=" ";
3210  break;
3211  case TK_WORD:
3212  case TK_LNKWORD:
3213  m_entry+=g_token->name;
3214  break;
3215  case TK_SYMBOL:
3216  {
3217  DocSymbol::SymType s = DocSymbol::decodeSymbol(g_token->name);
3218  switch (s)
3219  {
3220  case DocSymbol::Sym_BSlash: m_entry+='\\'; break;
3221  case DocSymbol::Sym_At: m_entry+='@'; break;
3222  case DocSymbol::Sym_Less: m_entry+='<'; break;
3223  case DocSymbol::Sym_Greater: m_entry+='>'; break;
3224  case DocSymbol::Sym_Amp: m_entry+='&'; break;
3225  case DocSymbol::Sym_Dollar: m_entry+='$'; break;
3226  case DocSymbol::Sym_Hash: m_entry+='#'; break;
3227  case DocSymbol::Sym_Percent: m_entry+='%'; break;
3228  case DocSymbol::Sym_apos: m_entry+='\''; break;
3229  case DocSymbol::Sym_Quot: m_entry+='"'; break;
3230  case DocSymbol::Sym_lsquo: m_entry+='`'; break;
3231  case DocSymbol::Sym_rsquo: m_entry+='\''; break;
3232  case DocSymbol::Sym_ldquo: m_entry+="``"; break;
3233  case DocSymbol::Sym_rdquo: m_entry+="''"; break;
3234  case DocSymbol::Sym_ndash: m_entry+="--"; break;
3235  case DocSymbol::Sym_mdash: m_entry+="---"; break;
3236  default:
3237  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected symbol found as argument of \\addindex");
3238  break;
3239  }
3240  }
3241  break;
3242  case TK_COMMAND:
3243  switch (Mappers::cmdMapper->map(g_token->name))
3244  {
3245  case CMD_BSLASH: m_entry+='\\'; break;
3246  case CMD_AT: m_entry+='@'; break;
3247  case CMD_LESS: m_entry+='<'; break;
3248  case CMD_GREATER: m_entry+='>'; break;
3249  case CMD_AMP: m_entry+='&'; break;
3250  case CMD_DOLLAR: m_entry+='$'; break;
3251  case CMD_HASH: m_entry+='#'; break;
3252  case CMD_DCOLON: m_entry+="::"; break;
3253  case CMD_PERCENT: m_entry+='%'; break;
3254  case CMD_NDASH: m_entry+="--"; break;
3255  case CMD_MDASH: m_entry+="---"; break;
3256  case CMD_QUOTE: m_entry+='"'; break;
3257  case CMD_PUNT: m_entry+='.'; break;
3258  case CMD_PLUS: m_entry+='+'; break;
3259  case CMD_MINUS: m_entry+='-'; break;
3260  default:
3261  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected command %s found as argument of \\addindex",
3262  qPrint(g_token->name));
3263  break;
3264  }
3265  break;
3266  default:
3267  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected token %s",
3268  tokToString(tok));
3269  break;
3270  }
3271  }
3272  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
3273  m_entry = m_entry.stripWhiteSpace();
3274 endindexentry:
3275  DBG(("DocIndexEntry::parse() end retval=%x\n",retval));
3276  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3277  ASSERT(n==this);
3278  return retval;
3279 }

3283 DocHtmlCaption::DocHtmlCaption(DocNode *parent,const HtmlAttribList &attribs)

3289  {
3290  if (opt->name=="id") // interpret id attribute as an anchor

3293  if (sec)

3296  m_file = sec->fileName;
3297  m_anchor = sec->label;

3299  if (g_sectionDict && g_sectionDict->find(opt->value)==0)
3300  {
3301  //printf("Inserting in dictionary!\n");
3302  g_sectionDict->append(opt->value,sec);
3303  }
3304  }
3305  else
3306  {
3307  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Invalid caption id `%s'",qPrint(opt->value));
3308  }

3310  else // copy attribute

3312  m_attribs.append(new HtmlAttrib(*opt));
3313  }

3317 
3318 int DocHtmlCaption::parse()
3319 {
3320  int retval=0;
3321  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3322  DBG(("DocHtmlCaption::parse() start\n"));
3323  int tok;
3324  while ((tok=doctokenizerYYlex()))
3325  {
3326  if (!defaultHandleToken(this,tok,m_children))
3327  {
3328  switch (tok)
3329  {
3330  case TK_COMMAND:
3331  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Illegal command %s as part of a <caption> tag",
3332  qPrint(g_token->name));
3333  break;
3334  case TK_SYMBOL:
3335  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unsupported symbol %s found",
3336  qPrint(g_token->name));
3337  break;
3338  case TK_HTMLTAG:
3339  {
3340  int tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
3341  if (tagId==HTML_CAPTION && g_token->endTag) // found </caption> tag
3342  {
3343  retval = RetVal_OK;
3344  goto endcaption;
3345  }
3346  else
3347  {
3348  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected html tag <%s%s> found within <caption> context",
3349  g_token->endTag?"/":"",qPrint(g_token->name));
3350  }
3351  }
3352  break;
3353  default:
3354  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected token %s",
3355  tokToString(tok));
3356  break;
3357  }
3358  }
3359  }
3360  if (tok==0)
3361  {
3362  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected end of comment while inside"
3363  " <caption> tag",doctokenizerYYlineno);
3364  }
3365 endcaption:
3366  handlePendingStyleCommands(this,m_children);
3367  DBG(("DocHtmlCaption::parse() end\n"));
3368  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3369  ASSERT(n==this);
3370  return retval;
3371 }

3375 int DocHtmlCell::parse()
3376 {
3377  int retval=RetVal_OK;
3378  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3379  DBG(("DocHtmlCell::parse() start\n"));
3380 
3381  // parse one or more paragraphs
3382  bool isFirst=TRUE;
3383  DocPara *par=0;
3384  do
3385  {
3386  par = new DocPara(this);
3387  if (isFirst) { par->markFirst(); isFirst=FALSE; }
3388  m_children.append(par);
3389  retval=par->parse();
3390  if (retval==TK_HTMLTAG)
3391  {
3392  int tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
3393  if (tagId==HTML_TD && g_token->endTag) // found </dt> tag
3394  {
3395  retval=TK_NEWPARA; // ignore the tag
3396  }
3397  else if (tagId==HTML_TH && g_token->endTag) // found </th> tag
3398  {
3399  retval=TK_NEWPARA; // ignore the tag
3400  }
3401  }
3402  }
3403  while (retval==TK_NEWPARA);
3404  if (par) par->markLast();
3405 
3406  DBG(("DocHtmlCell::parse() end\n"));
3407  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3408  ASSERT(n==this);
3409  return retval;
3410 }

3449 int DocHtmlCell::rowSpan() const
3450 {
3451  int retval = 0;
3452  HtmlAttribList attrs = attribs();
3453  uint i;
3454  for (i=0; i<attrs.count(); ++i)
3455  {
3456  if (attrs.at(i)->name.lower()=="rowspan")
3457  {
3458  retval = attrs.at(i)->value.toInt();
3459  break;
3460  }
3461  }
3462  return retval;
3463 }

3465 int DocHtmlCell::colSpan() const
3466 {
3467  int retval = 1;
3468  HtmlAttribList attrs = attribs();
3469  uint i;
3470  for (i=0; i<attrs.count(); ++i)
3471  {
3472  if (attrs.at(i)->name.lower()=="colspan")
3473  {
3474  retval = QMAX(1,attrs.at(i)->value.toInt());
3475  break;
3476  }
3477  }
3478  return retval;
3479 }

3481 DocHtmlCell::Alignment DocHtmlCell::alignment() const
3482 {
3483  HtmlAttribList attrs = attribs();
3484  uint i;
3485  for (i=0; i<attrs.count(); ++i)
3486  {
3487  if (attrs.at(i)->name.lower()=="align")
3488  {
3489  if (attrs.at(i)->value.lower()=="center")
3490  return Center;
3491  else if (attrs.at(i)->value.lower()=="right")
3492  return Right;
3493  else return Left;
3494  }
3495  }
3496  return Left;
3497 }

3501 
3502 int DocHtmlRow::parse()
3503 {
3504  int retval=RetVal_OK;
3505  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3506  DBG(("DocHtmlRow::parse() start\n"));
3507 
3508  bool isHeading=FALSE;
3509  bool isFirst=TRUE;
3510  DocHtmlCell *cell=0;
3511 
3512  // get next token
3513  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3514  // skip whitespace
3515  while (tok==TK_WHITESPACE || tok==TK_NEWPARA) tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3516  // should find a html tag now
3517  if (tok==TK_HTMLTAG)
3518  {
3519  int tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
3520  if (tagId==HTML_TD && !g_token->endTag) // found <td> tag
3521  {
3522  }
3523  else if (tagId==HTML_TH && !g_token->endTag) // found <th> tag
3524  {
3525  isHeading=TRUE;
3526  }
3527  else // found some other tag
3528  {
3529  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <td> or <th> tag but "
3530  "found <%s> instead!",qPrint(g_token->name));
3531  doctokenizerYYpushBackHtmlTag(g_token->name);
3532  goto endrow;
3533  }
3534  }
3535  else if (tok==0) // premature end of comment
3536  {
3537  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment while looking"
3538  " for a html description title");
3539  goto endrow;
3540  }
3541  else // token other than html token
3542  {
3543  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <td> or <th> tag but found %s token instead!",
3544  tokToString(tok));
3545  goto endrow;
3546  }
3547 
3548  // parse one or more cells
3549  do
3550  {
3551  cell=new DocHtmlCell(this,g_token->attribs,isHeading);
3552  cell->markFirst(isFirst);
3553  isFirst=FALSE;
3554  m_children.append(cell);
3555  retval=cell->parse();
3556  isHeading = retval==RetVal_TableHCell;
3557  }
3558  while (retval==RetVal_TableCell || retval==RetVal_TableHCell);
3559  if (cell) cell->markLast(TRUE);
3560 
3561 endrow:
3562  DBG(("DocHtmlRow::parse() end\n"));
3563  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3564  ASSERT(n==this);
3565  return retval;
3566 }

3598  }
3599  else if (tok==0) // premature end of comment
3600  {

3630 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3631 
3632 int DocHtmlTable::parse()
3633 {
3634  int retval=RetVal_OK;
3635  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3636  DBG(("DocHtmlTable::parse() start\n"));
3637 
3638 getrow:
3639  // get next token
3640  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3641  // skip whitespace
3642  while (tok==TK_WHITESPACE || tok==TK_NEWPARA) tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3643  // should find a html tag now
3644  if (tok==TK_HTMLTAG)
3645  {
3646  int tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
3647  if (tagId==HTML_TR && !g_token->endTag) // found <tr> tag
3648  {
3649  // no caption, just rows
3650  retval=RetVal_TableRow;
3651  }
3652  else if (tagId==HTML_CAPTION && !g_token->endTag) // found <caption> tag
3653  {
3654  if (m_caption)
3655  {
3656  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"table already has a caption, found another one");
3657  }
3658  else
3659  {
3660  m_caption = new DocHtmlCaption(this,g_token->attribs);
3661  retval=m_caption->parse();
3662 
3663  if (retval==RetVal_OK) // caption was parsed ok
3664  {
3665  goto getrow;
3666  }
3667  }
3668  }
3669  else // found wrong token
3670  {
3671  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <tr> or <caption> tag but "
3672  "found <%s%s> instead!", g_token->endTag ? "/" : "", qPrint(g_token->name));
3673  }
3674  }
3675  else if (tok==0) // premature end of comment
3676  {
3677  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment while looking"
3678  " for a <tr> or <caption> tag");
3679  }
3680  else // token other than html token
3681  {
3682  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <tr> tag but found %s token instead!",
3683  tokToString(tok));
3684  }
3685 
3686  // parse one or more rows
3687  while (retval==RetVal_TableRow)
3688  {
3689  DocHtmlRow *tr=new DocHtmlRow(this,g_token->attribs);
3690  m_children.append(tr);
3691  retval=tr->parse();
3692  }
3693 
3694  computeTableGrid();
3695 
3696  DBG(("DocHtmlTable::parse() end\n"));
3697  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3698  ASSERT(n==this);
3699  return retval==RetVal_EndTable ? RetVal_OK : retval;
3700 }

3702 int DocHtmlTable::parseXml()
3703 {
3704  int retval=RetVal_OK;
3705  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3706  DBG(("DocHtmlTable::parseXml() start\n"));
3707 
3708  // get next token
3709  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3710  // skip whitespace
3711  while (tok==TK_WHITESPACE || tok==TK_NEWPARA) tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3712  // should find a html tag now
3713  int tagId=0;
3714  bool isHeader=FALSE;
3715  if (tok==TK_HTMLTAG)
3716  {
3717  tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
3718  if (tagId==XML_ITEM && !g_token->endTag) // found <item> tag
3719  {
3720  retval=RetVal_TableRow;
3721  }
3722  if (tagId==XML_LISTHEADER && !g_token->endTag) // found <listheader> tag
3723  {
3724  retval=RetVal_TableRow;
3725  isHeader=TRUE;
3726  }
3727  }
3728 
3729  // parse one or more rows
3730  while (retval==RetVal_TableRow)
3731  {
3732  DocHtmlRow *tr=new DocHtmlRow(this,g_token->attribs);
3733  m_children.append(tr);
3734  retval=tr->parseXml(isHeader);
3735  isHeader=FALSE;
3736  }
3737 
3738  computeTableGrid();
3739 
3740  DBG(("DocHtmlTable::parseXml() end\n"));
3741  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3742  ASSERT(n==this);
3743  tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
3744  return tagId==XML_LIST && g_token->endTag ? RetVal_OK : retval;
3745 }

3748 struct ActiveRowSpan
3749 {
3750  ActiveRowSpan(int rows,int col) : rowsLeft(rows), column(col) {}
3751  int rowsLeft;
3752  int column;
3753 };
3754 
3756 typedef QList<ActiveRowSpan> RowSpanList;
3757 
3762 void DocHtmlTable::computeTableGrid()
3763 {
3764  //printf("computeTableGrid()\n");
3765  RowSpanList rowSpans;
3766  rowSpans.setAutoDelete(TRUE);
3767  int maxCols=0;
3768  int rowIdx=1;
3769  QListIterator<DocNode> li(children());
3770  DocNode *rowNode;
3771  for (li.toFirst();(rowNode=li.current());++li)
3772  {
3773  int colIdx=1;
3774  int cells=0;
3775  if (rowNode->kind()==DocNode::Kind_HtmlRow)
3776  {
3777  uint i;
3778  DocHtmlRow *row = (DocHtmlRow*)rowNode;
3779  QListIterator<DocNode> rli(row->children());
3780  DocNode *cellNode;
3781  for (rli.toFirst();(cellNode=rli.current());++rli)
3782  {
3783  if (cellNode->kind()==DocNode::Kind_HtmlCell)
3784  {
3785  DocHtmlCell *cell = (DocHtmlCell*)cellNode;
3786  int rs = cell->rowSpan();
3787  int cs = cell->colSpan();
3788 
3789  for (i=0;i<rowSpans.count();i++)
3790  {
3791  if (rowSpans.at(i)->rowsLeft>0 &&
3792  rowSpans.at(i)->column==colIdx)
3793  {
3794  colIdx=rowSpans.at(i)->column+1;
3795  cells++;
3796  }
3797  }
3798  if (rs>0) rowSpans.append(new ActiveRowSpan(rs,colIdx));
3799  //printf("found cell at (%d,%d)\n",rowIdx,colIdx);
3800  cell->setRowIndex(rowIdx);
3801  cell->setColumnIndex(colIdx);
3802  colIdx+=cs;
3803  cells++;
3804  }
3805  }
3806  for (i=0;i<rowSpans.count();i++)
3807  {
3808  if (rowSpans.at(i)->rowsLeft>0) rowSpans.at(i)->rowsLeft--;
3809  }
3810  row->setVisibleCells(cells);
3811  row->setRowIndex(rowIdx);
3812  rowIdx++;
3813  }
3814  if (colIdx-1>maxCols) maxCols=colIdx-1;
3815  }
3816  m_numCols = maxCols;
3817 }
3818 
3819 void DocHtmlTable::accept(DocVisitor *v)
3820 {
3821  v->visitPre(this);
3822  // for HTML output we put the caption first
3823  //if (m_caption && v->id()==DocVisitor_Html) m_caption->accept(v);
3824  // doxygen 1.8.11: always put the caption first
3825  if (m_caption) m_caption->accept(v);
3826  QListIterator<DocNode> cli(m_children);
3827  DocNode *n;
3828  for (cli.toFirst();(n=cli.current());++cli) n->accept(v);
3829  // for other output formats we put the caption last
3830  //if (m_caption && v->id()!=DocVisitor_Html) m_caption->accept(v);
3831  v->visitPost(this);
3832 }

3834 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3835 
3836 int DocHtmlDescTitle::parse()
3837 {
3838  int retval=0;
3839  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3840  DBG(("DocHtmlDescTitle::parse() start\n"));
3841 
3842  int tok;
3843  while ((tok=doctokenizerYYlex()))
3844  {
3845  if (!defaultHandleToken(this,tok,m_children))
3846  {
3847  switch (tok)
3848  {
3849  case TK_COMMAND:
3850  {
3851  QCString cmdName=g_token->name;
3852  bool isJavaLink=FALSE;
3853  switch (Mappers::cmdMapper->map(cmdName))
3854  {
3855  case CMD_REF:
3856  {
3857  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3858  if (tok!=TK_WHITESPACE)
3859  {
3860  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected whitespace after %s command",
3861  qPrint(g_token->name));
3862  }
3863  else
3864  {
3865  doctokenizerYYsetStateRef();
3866  tok=doctokenizerYYlex(); // get the reference id
3867  if (tok!=TK_WORD)
3868  {
3869  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected token %s as the argument of %s",
3870  tokToString(tok),qPrint(cmdName));
3871  }
3872  else
3873  {
3874  DocRef *ref = new DocRef(this,g_token->name,g_context);
3875  m_children.append(ref);
3876  ref->parse();
3877  }
3878  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
3879  }
3880  }
3881  break;
3882  case CMD_JAVALINK:
3883  isJavaLink=TRUE;
3884  // fall through
3885  case CMD_LINK:
3886  {
3887  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3888  if (tok!=TK_WHITESPACE)
3889  {
3890  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected whitespace after %s command",
3891  qPrint(cmdName));
3892  }
3893  else
3894  {
3895  doctokenizerYYsetStateLink();
3896  tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
3897  if (tok!=TK_WORD)
3898  {
3899  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected token %s as the argument of %s",
3900  tokToString(tok),qPrint(cmdName));
3901  }
3902  else
3903  {
3904  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
3905  DocLink *lnk = new DocLink(this,g_token->name);
3906  m_children.append(lnk);
3907  QCString leftOver = lnk->parse(isJavaLink);
3908  if (!leftOver.isEmpty())
3909  {
3910  m_children.append(new DocWord(this,leftOver));
3911  }
3912  }
3913  }
3914  }
3915 
3916  break;
3917  default:
3918  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Illegal command %s as part of a <dt> tag",
3919  qPrint(g_token->name));
3920  }
3921  }
3922  break;
3923  case TK_SYMBOL:
3924  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unsupported symbol %s found",
3925  qPrint(g_token->name));
3926  break;
3927  case TK_HTMLTAG:
3928  {
3929  int tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
3930  if (tagId==HTML_DD && !g_token->endTag) // found <dd> tag
3931  {
3932  retval = RetVal_DescData;
3933  goto endtitle;
3934  }
3935  else if (tagId==HTML_DT && g_token->endTag)
3936  {
3937  // ignore </dt> tag.
3938  }
3939  else if (tagId==HTML_DT)
3940  {
3941  // missing <dt> tag.
3942  retval = RetVal_DescTitle;
3943  goto endtitle;
3944  }
3945  else if (tagId==HTML_DL && g_token->endTag)
3946  {
3947  retval=RetVal_EndDesc;
3948  goto endtitle;
3949  }
3950  else if (tagId==HTML_A)
3951  {
3952  if (!g_token->endTag)
3953  {
3954  handleAHref(this,m_children,g_token->attribs);
3955  }
3956  }
3957  else
3958  {
3959  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected html tag <%s%s> found within <dt> context",
3960  g_token->endTag?"/":"",qPrint(g_token->name));
3961  }
3962  }
3963  break;
3964  default:
3965  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected token %s",
3966  tokToString(tok));
3967  break;
3968  }
3969  }
3970  }
3971  if (tok==0)
3972  {
3973  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected end of comment while inside"
3974  " <dt> tag");
3975  }
3976 endtitle:
3977  handlePendingStyleCommands(this,m_children);
3978  DBG(("DocHtmlDescTitle::parse() end\n"));
3979  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
3980  ASSERT(n==this);
3981  return retval;
3982 }
3983 
3984 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3985 
3986 int DocHtmlDescData::parse()
3987 {
3988  m_attribs = g_token->attribs;
3989  int retval=0;
3990  g_nodeStack.push(this);
3991  DBG(("DocHtmlDescData::parse() start\n"));
3992 
3993  bool isFirst=TRUE;
3994  DocPara *par=0;
3995  do
3996  {
3997  par = new DocPara(this);
3998  if (isFirst) { par->markFirst(); isFirst=FALSE; }
3999  m_children.append(par);
4000  retval=par->parse();
4001  }
4002  while (retval==TK_NEWPARA);
4003  if (par) par->markLast();
4004 
4005  DBG(("DocHtmlDescData::parse() end\n"));
4006  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4007  ASSERT(n==this);
4008  return retval;
4009 }

4011 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4012 
4013 int DocHtmlDescList::parse()
4014 {
4015  int retval=RetVal_OK;
4016  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4017  DBG(("DocHtmlDescList::parse() start\n"));
4018 
4019  // get next token
4020  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4021  // skip whitespace
4022  while (tok==TK_WHITESPACE || tok==TK_NEWPARA) tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4023  // should find a html tag now
4024  if (tok==TK_HTMLTAG)
4025  {
4026  int tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
4027  if (tagId==HTML_DT && !g_token->endTag) // found <dt> tag
4028  {
4029  // continue
4030  }
4031  else // found some other tag
4032  {
4033  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <dt> tag but "
4034  "found <%s> instead!",qPrint(g_token->name));
4035  doctokenizerYYpushBackHtmlTag(g_token->name);
4036  goto enddesclist;
4037  }
4038  }
4039  else if (tok==0) // premature end of comment
4040  {
4041  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment while looking"
4042  " for a html description title");
4043  goto enddesclist;
4044  }
4045  else // token other than html token
4046  {
4047  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <dt> tag but found %s token instead!",
4048  tokToString(tok));
4049  goto enddesclist;
4050  }
4051 
4052  do
4053  {
4054  DocHtmlDescTitle *dt=new DocHtmlDescTitle(this,g_token->attribs);
4055  m_children.append(dt);
4056  DocHtmlDescData *dd=new DocHtmlDescData(this);
4057  m_children.append(dd);
4058  retval=dt->parse();
4059  if (retval==RetVal_DescData)
4060  {
4061  retval=dd->parse();
4062  }
4063  else if (retval!=RetVal_DescTitle)
4064  {
4065  // error
4066  break;
4067  }
4068  } while (retval==RetVal_DescTitle);
4069 
4070  if (retval==0)
4071  {
4072  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment while inside <dl> block");
4073  }
4074 
4075 enddesclist:
4076 
4077  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4078  ASSERT(n==this);
4079  DBG(("DocHtmlDescList::parse() end\n"));
4080  return retval==RetVal_EndDesc ? RetVal_OK : retval;
4081 }

4144 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4145 
4146 int DocHtmlList::parse()
4147 {
4148  DBG(("DocHtmlList::parse() start\n"));
4149  int retval=RetVal_OK;
4150  int num=1;
4151  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4152 
4153  // get next token
4154  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4155  // skip whitespace and paragraph breaks
4156  while (tok==TK_WHITESPACE || tok==TK_NEWPARA) tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4157  // should find a html tag now
4158  if (tok==TK_HTMLTAG)
4159  {
4160  int tagId=Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name);
4161  if (tagId==HTML_LI && !g_token->endTag) // found <li> tag
4162  {
4163  // ok, we can go on.
4164  }
4165  else if (((m_type==Unordered && tagId==HTML_UL) ||
4166  (m_type==Ordered && tagId==HTML_OL)
4167  ) && g_token->endTag
4168  ) // found empty list
4169  {
4170  // add dummy item to obtain valid HTML
4171  m_children.append(new DocHtmlListItem(this,HtmlAttribList(),1));
4172  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"empty list!");
4173  retval = RetVal_EndList;
4174  goto endlist;
4175  }
4176  else // found some other tag
4177  {
4178  // add dummy item to obtain valid HTML
4179  m_children.append(new DocHtmlListItem(this,HtmlAttribList(),1));
4180  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <li> tag but "
4181  "found <%s%s> instead!",g_token->endTag?"/":"",qPrint(g_token->name));
4182  doctokenizerYYpushBackHtmlTag(g_token->name);
4183  goto endlist;
4184  }
4185  }
4186  else if (tok==0) // premature end of comment
4187  {
4188  // add dummy item to obtain valid HTML
4189  m_children.append(new DocHtmlListItem(this,HtmlAttribList(),1));
4190  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment while looking"
4191  " for a html list item");
4192  goto endlist;
4193  }
4194  else // token other than html token
4195  {
4196  // add dummy item to obtain valid HTML
4197  m_children.append(new DocHtmlListItem(this,HtmlAttribList(),1));
4198  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected <li> tag but found %s token instead!",
4199  tokToString(tok));
4200  goto endlist;
4201  }
4202 
4203  do
4204  {
4205  DocHtmlListItem *li=new DocHtmlListItem(this,g_token->attribs,num++);
4206  m_children.append(li);
4207  retval=li->parse();
4208  } while (retval==RetVal_ListItem);
4209 
4210  if (retval==0)
4211  {
4212  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment while inside <%cl> block",
4213  m_type==Unordered ? 'u' : 'o');
4214  }
4215 
4216 endlist:
4217  DBG(("DocHtmlList::parse() end retval=%x\n",retval));
4218  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4219  ASSERT(n==this);
4220  return retval==RetVal_EndList ? RetVal_OK : retval;
4221 }

4224 {

4232  // skip whitespace and paragraph breaks
4233  while (tok==TK_WHITESPACE || tok==TK_NEWPARA) tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4234  // should find a html tag now

4276  m_type==Unordered ? "bullet" : "number");
4277  }
4278 
4279 endlist:
4280  DBG(("DocHtmlList::parseXml() end retval=%x\n",retval));

4284  (retval==RetVal_CloseXml || g_token->name=="list") ?

4380 int DocAutoListItem::parse()
4381 {
4382  int retval = RetVal_OK;
4383  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4384 
4385  // first parse any number of paragraphs
4386  bool isFirst=TRUE;
4387  DocPara *lastPar=0;
4388  do
4389  {
4390  DocPara *par = new DocPara(this);
4391  if (isFirst) { par->markFirst(); isFirst=FALSE; }
4392  retval=par->parse();
4393  if (!par->isEmpty())
4394  {
4395  m_children.append(par);
4396  if (lastPar) lastPar->markLast(FALSE);
4397  lastPar=par;
4398  }
4399  else
4400  {
4401  delete par;
4402  }
4403  // next paragraph should be more indented than the - marker to belong
4404  // to this item
4405  } while (retval==TK_NEWPARA && g_token->indent>m_indent);
4406  if (lastPar) lastPar->markLast();
4407 
4408  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4409  ASSERT(n==this);
4410  //printf("DocAutoListItem: retval=%d indent=%d\n",retval,g_token->indent);
4411  return retval;
4412 }

4424 int DocAutoList::parse()
4425 {
4426  int retval = RetVal_OK;
4427  int num=1;
4428  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4429  doctokenizerYYstartAutoList();
4430  // first item or sub list => create new list
4431  do
4432  {
4433  if (g_token->id!=-1) // explicitly numbered list
4434  {
4435  num=g_token->id; // override num with real number given
4436  }
4437  DocAutoListItem *li = new DocAutoListItem(this,m_indent,num++);
4438  m_children.append(li);
4439  retval=li->parse();
4440  //printf("DocAutoList::parse(): retval=0x%x g_token->indent=%d m_indent=%d "
4441  // "m_isEnumList=%d g_token->isEnumList=%d g_token->name=%s\n",
4442  // retval,g_token->indent,m_indent,m_isEnumList,g_token->isEnumList,
4443  // g_token->name.data());
4444  //printf("num=%d g_token->id=%d\n",num,g_token->id);
4445  }
4446  while (retval==TK_LISTITEM && // new list item
4447  m_indent==g_token->indent && // at same indent level
4448  m_isEnumList==g_token->isEnumList && // of the same kind
4449  (g_token->id==-1 || g_token->id>=num) // increasing number (or no number)
4450  );
4451 
4452  doctokenizerYYendAutoList();
4453  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4454  ASSERT(n==this);
4455  return retval;
4456 }

4458 //--------------------------------------------------------------------------
4459 
4460 void DocTitle::parse()
4461 {
4462  DBG(("DocTitle::parse() start\n"));
4463  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4464  doctokenizerYYsetStateTitle();
4465  int tok;
4466  while ((tok=doctokenizerYYlex()))
4467  {
4468  if (!defaultHandleToken(this,tok,m_children))
4469  {
4470  switch (tok)
4471  {
4472  case TK_COMMAND:
4473  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Illegal command %s as part of a title section",
4474  qPrint(g_token->name));
4475  break;
4476  case TK_SYMBOL:
4477  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unsupported symbol %s found",
4478  qPrint(g_token->name));
4479  break;
4480  default:
4481  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected token %s",
4482  tokToString(tok));
4483  break;
4484  }
4485  }
4486  }
4487  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
4488  handlePendingStyleCommands(this,m_children);
4489  DBG(("DocTitle::parse() end\n"));
4490  DocNode *n = g_nodeStack.pop();
4491  ASSERT(n==this);
4492 }
4493

4495 {
4496  m_children.append(new DocWord(this,text));
4497 }

4513 void DocSimpleSect::accept(DocVisitor *v)
4514 {
4515  v->visitPre(this);
4516  if (m_title) m_title->accept(v);
4517  QListIterator<DocNode> cli(m_children);
4518  DocNode *n;
4519  for (cli.toFirst();(n=cli.current());++cli) n->accept(v);
4520  v->visitPost(this);
4521 }
4522 
4523 int DocSimpleSect::parse(bool userTitle,bool needsSeparator)
4524 {
4525  DBG(("DocSimpleSect::parse() start\n"));
4526  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4527 
4528  // handle case for user defined title
4529  if (userTitle)
4530  {
4531  m_title = new DocTitle(this);
4532  m_title->parse();
4533  }
4534 
4535  // add new paragraph as child
4536  DocPara *par = new DocPara(this);
4537  if (m_children.isEmpty())
4538  {
4539  par->markFirst();
4540  }
4541  else
4542  {
4543  ASSERT(m_children.getLast()->kind()==DocNode::Kind_Para);
4544  ((DocPara *)m_children.getLast())->markLast(FALSE);
4545  }
4546  par->markLast();
4547  if (needsSeparator) m_children.append(new DocSimpleSectSep(this));
4548  m_children.append(par);
4549 
4550  // parse the contents of the paragraph
4551  int retval = par->parse();
4552 
4553  DBG(("DocSimpleSect::parse() end retval=%d\n",retval));
4554  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4555  ASSERT(n==this);
4556  return retval; // 0==EOF, TK_NEWPARA, TK_LISTITEM, TK_ENDLIST, RetVal_SimpleSec
4557 }

4565  m_title->parseFromString(g_token->name);
4566

4571

4578 int DocSimpleSect::parseXml()
4579 {
4580  DBG(("DocSimpleSect::parse() start\n"));
4581  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4582 
4583  int retval = RetVal_OK;
4584  for (;;)
4585  {
4586  // add new paragraph as child
4587  DocPara *par = new DocPara(this);
4588  if (m_children.isEmpty())
4589  {
4590  par->markFirst();
4591  }
4592  else
4593  {
4594  ASSERT(m_children.getLast()->kind()==DocNode::Kind_Para);
4595  ((DocPara *)m_children.getLast())->markLast(FALSE);
4596  }
4597  par->markLast();
4598  m_children.append(par);
4599 
4600  // parse the contents of the paragraph
4601  retval = par->parse();
4602  if (retval == 0) break;
4603  if (retval == RetVal_CloseXml)
4604  {
4605  retval = RetVal_OK;
4606  break;
4607  }
4608  }
4609 
4610  DBG(("DocSimpleSect::parseXml() end retval=%d\n",retval));
4611  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4612  ASSERT(n==this);
4613  return retval;
4614 }

4616 void DocSimpleSect::appendLinkWord(const QCString &word)
4617 {
4618  DocPara *p;
4619  if (m_children.isEmpty() || m_children.getLast()->kind()!=DocNode::Kind_Para)
4620  {
4621  p = new DocPara(this);
4622  m_children.append(p);
4623  }
4624  else
4625  {
4626  p = (DocPara *)m_children.getLast();
4627 
4628  // Comma-seperate <seealso> links.
4629  p->injectToken(TK_WORD,",");
4630  p->injectToken(TK_WHITESPACE," ");
4631  }
4632 
4633  g_inSeeBlock=TRUE;
4634  p->injectToken(TK_LNKWORD,word);
4635  g_inSeeBlock=FALSE;
4636 }
4637 
4638 QCString DocSimpleSect::typeString() const
4639 {
4640  switch (m_type)
4641  {
4642  case Unknown: break;
4643  case See: return "see";
4644  case Return: return "return";
4645  case Author: // fall through
4646  case Authors: return "author";
4647  case Version: return "version";
4648  case Since: return "since";
4649  case Date: return "date";
4650  case Note: return "note";
4651  case Warning: return "warning";
4652  case Pre: return "pre";
4653  case Post: return "post";
4654  case Copyright: return "copyright";
4655  case Invar: return "invariant";
4656  case Remark: return "remark";
4657  case Attention: return "attention";
4658  case User: return "user";
4659  case Rcs: return "rcs";
4660  }
4661  return "unknown";
4662 }
4663 
4664 //--------------------------------------------------------------------------
4665 
4666 int DocParamList::parse(const QCString &cmdName)
4667 {
4668  int retval=RetVal_OK;
4669  DBG(("DocParamList::parse() start\n"));
4670  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4671  DocPara *par=0;
4672  QCString saveCmdName = cmdName;
4673 
4674  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4675  if (tok!=TK_WHITESPACE)
4676  {
4677  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected whitespace after %s command",
4678  qPrint(cmdName));
4679  retval=0;
4680  goto endparamlist;
4681  }
4682  doctokenizerYYsetStateParam();
4683  tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4684  while (tok==TK_WORD) /* there is a parameter name */
4685  {
4686  if (m_type==DocParamSect::Param)
4687  {
4688  int typeSeparator = g_token->name.find('#'); // explicit type position
4689  if (typeSeparator!=-1)
4690  {
4691  handleParameterType(this,m_paramTypes,g_token->name.left(typeSeparator));
4692  g_token->name = g_token->name.mid(typeSeparator+1);
4693  g_hasParamCommand=TRUE;
4694  checkArgumentName(g_token->name,TRUE);
4695  ((DocParamSect*)parent())->m_hasTypeSpecifier=TRUE;
4696  }
4697  else
4698  {
4699  g_hasParamCommand=TRUE;
4700  checkArgumentName(g_token->name,TRUE);
4701  }
4702  }
4703  else if (m_type==DocParamSect::RetVal)
4704  {
4705  g_hasReturnCommand=TRUE;
4706  checkArgumentName(g_token->name,FALSE);
4707  }
4708  //m_params.append(g_token->name);
4709  handleLinkedWord(this,m_params);
4710  tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4711  }
4712  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
4713  if (tok==0) /* premature end of comment block */
4714  {
4715  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment block while parsing the "
4716  "argument of command %s",qPrint(cmdName));
4717  retval=0;
4718  goto endparamlist;
4719  }
4720  if (tok!=TK_WHITESPACE) /* premature end of comment block */
4721  {
4722  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected token in comment block while parsing the "
4723  "argument of command %s",qPrint(saveCmdName));
4724  retval=0;
4725  goto endparamlist;
4726  }
4727 
4728  par = new DocPara(this);
4729  m_paragraphs.append(par);
4730  retval = par->parse();
4731  par->markFirst();
4732  par->markLast();
4733 
4734 endparamlist:
4735  DBG(("DocParamList::parse() end retval=%d\n",retval));
4736  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4737  ASSERT(n==this);
4738  return retval;
4739 }
4740 
4741 int DocParamList::parseXml(const QCString &paramName)
4742 {
4743  int retval=RetVal_OK;
4744  DBG(("DocParamList::parseXml() start\n"));
4745  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4746 
4747  g_token->name = paramName;
4748  if (m_type==DocParamSect::Param)
4749  {
4750  g_hasParamCommand=TRUE;
4751  checkArgumentName(g_token->name,TRUE);
4752  }
4753  else if (m_type==DocParamSect::RetVal)
4754  {
4755  g_hasReturnCommand=TRUE;
4756  checkArgumentName(g_token->name,FALSE);
4757  }
4758 
4759  handleLinkedWord(this,m_params);
4760 
4761  do
4762  {
4763  DocPara *par = new DocPara(this);
4764  retval = par->parse();
4765  if (par->isEmpty()) // avoid adding an empty paragraph for the whitespace
4766  // after </para> and before </param>
4767  {
4768  delete par;
4769  break;
4770  }
4771  else // append the paragraph to the list
4772  {
4773  if (m_paragraphs.isEmpty())
4774  {
4775  par->markFirst();
4776  }
4777  else
4778  {
4779  m_paragraphs.getLast()->markLast(FALSE);
4780  }
4781  par->markLast();
4782  m_paragraphs.append(par);
4783  }
4784 
4785  if (retval == 0) break;
4786 
4787  } while (retval==RetVal_CloseXml &&
4788  Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name)!=XML_PARAM &&
4789  Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name)!=XML_TYPEPARAM &&
4790  Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(g_token->name)!=XML_EXCEPTION);
4791 
4792 
4793  if (retval==0) /* premature end of comment block */
4794  {
4795  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unterminated param or exception tag");
4796  }
4797  else
4798  {
4799  retval=RetVal_OK;
4800  }
4801 
4802 
4803  DBG(("DocParamList::parse() end retval=%d\n",retval));
4804  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4805  ASSERT(n==this);
4806  return retval;
4807 }

4809 //--------------------------------------------------------------------------
4810 
4811 int DocParamSect::parse(const QCString &cmdName,bool xmlContext, Direction d)
4812 {
4813  int retval=RetVal_OK;
4814  DBG(("DocParamSect::parse() start\n"));
4815  g_nodeStack.push(this);
4816 
4817  if (d!=Unspecified)
4818  {
4819  m_hasInOutSpecifier=TRUE;
4820  }
4821 
4822  DocParamList *pl = new DocParamList(this,m_type,d);
4823  if (m_children.isEmpty())
4824  {
4825  pl->markFirst();
4826  pl->markLast();
4827  }
4828  else
4829  {
4830  ASSERT(m_children.getLast()->kind()==DocNode::Kind_ParamList);
4831  ((DocParamList *)m_children.getLast())->markLast(FALSE);
4832  pl->markLast();
4833  }
4834  m_children.append(pl);
4835  if (xmlContext)
4836  {
4837  retval = pl->parseXml(cmdName);
4838  }
4839  else
4840  {
4841  retval = pl->parse(cmdName);
4842  }
4843  if (retval==RetVal_EndParBlock)
4844  {
4845  retval = RetVal_OK;
4846  }
4847 
4848  DBG(("DocParamSect::parse() end retval=%d\n",retval));
4849  DocNode *n=g_nodeStack.pop();
4850  ASSERT(n==this);
4851  return retval;
4852 }

4855 
4856 int DocPara::handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Type t, bool xmlContext)
4857 {
4858  DocSimpleSect *ss=0;
4859  bool needsSeparator = FALSE;
4860  if (!m_children.isEmpty() && // previous element
4861  m_children.getLast()->kind()==Kind_SimpleSect && // was a simple sect
4862  ((DocSimpleSect *)m_children.getLast())->type()==t && // of same type
4863  t!=DocSimpleSect::User) // but not user defined
4864  {
4865  // append to previous section
4866  ss=(DocSimpleSect *)m_children.getLast();
4867  needsSeparator = TRUE;
4868  }
4869  else // start new section
4870  {
4871  ss=new DocSimpleSect(this,t);
4872  m_children.append(ss);
4873  }
4874  int rv = RetVal_OK;
4875  if (xmlContext)
4876  {
4877  return ss->parseXml();
4878  }
4879  else
4880  {
4881  rv = ss->parse(t==DocSimpleSect::User,needsSeparator);
4882  }
4883  return (rv!=TK_NEWPARA) ? rv : RetVal_OK;
4884 }

4888  bool xmlContext=FALSE,
4889  int direction=DocParamSect::Unspecified)

4891  DocParamSect *ps=0;

4893  m_children.getLast()->kind()==Kind_ParamSect && // was a param sect
4894  ((DocParamSect *)m_children.getLast())->type()==t) // of same type
4895  {
4896  // append to previous section
4897  ps=(DocParamSect *)m_children.getLast();
4898  }
4899  else // start new section
4900  {
4901  ps=new DocParamSect(this,t);
4902  m_children.append(ps);
4903  }
4904  int rv=ps->parse(cmdName,xmlContext,(DocParamSect::Direction)direction);
4905  return (rv!=TK_NEWPARA) ? rv : RetVal_OK;
4906 }

4962 void DocPara::handleIncludeOperator(const QCString &cmdName,DocIncOperator::Type t)
4963 {
4964  DBG(("handleIncludeOperator(%s)\n",qPrint(cmdName)));
4965  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4966  if (tok!=TK_WHITESPACE)
4967  {
4968  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected whitespace after %s command",
4969  qPrint(cmdName));
4970  return;
4971  }
4972  doctokenizerYYsetStatePattern();
4973  tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
4974  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
4975  if (tok==0)
4976  {
4977  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment block while parsing the "
4978  "argument of command %s", qPrint(cmdName));
4979  return;
4980  }
4981  else if (tok!=TK_WORD)
4982  {
4983  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected token %s as the argument of %s",
4984  tokToString(tok),qPrint(cmdName));
4985  return;
4986  }
4987  DocIncOperator *op = new DocIncOperator(this,t,g_token->name,g_context,g_isExample,g_exampleName);
4988  QListIterator<DocNode> it(m_children);
4989  DocNode *n1 = it.toLast();
4990  --it;
4991  DocNode *n2 = n1!=0 ? it.current() : 0;
4992  bool isFirst = n1==0 || // no last node
4993  (n1->kind()!=DocNode::Kind_IncOperator &&
4994  n1->kind()!=DocNode::Kind_WhiteSpace
4995  ) || // last node is not operator or whitespace
4996  (n1->kind()==DocNode::Kind_WhiteSpace &&
4997  n2!=0 && n2->kind()!=DocNode::Kind_IncOperator
4998  ); // previous not is not operator
4999  op->markFirst(isFirst);
5000  op->markLast(TRUE);
5001  if (n1!=0 && n1->kind()==DocNode::Kind_IncOperator)
5002  {
5003  ((DocIncOperator *)n1)->markLast(FALSE);
5004  }
5005  else if (n1!=0 && n1->kind()==DocNode::Kind_WhiteSpace &&
5006  n2!=0 && n2->kind()==DocNode::Kind_IncOperator
5007  )
5008  {
5009  ((DocIncOperator *)n2)->markLast(FALSE);
5010  }
5011  m_children.append(op);
5012  op->parse();
5013 }

5151 void DocPara::handleInclude(const QCString &cmdName,DocInclude::Type t)
5152 {
5153  DBG(("handleInclude(%s)\n",qPrint(cmdName)));
5154  int tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
5155  if (tok!=TK_WHITESPACE)
5156  {
5157  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected whitespace after %s command",
5158  qPrint(cmdName));
5159  return;
5160  }
5161  doctokenizerYYsetStateFile();
5162  tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
5163  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
5164  if (tok==0)
5165  {
5166  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected end of comment block while parsing the "
5167  "argument of command %s",qPrint(cmdName));
5168  return;
5169  }
5170  else if (tok!=TK_WORD)
5171  {
5172  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected token %s as the argument of %s",
5173  tokToString(tok),qPrint(cmdName));
5174  return;
5175  }
5176  QCString fileName = g_token->name;
5177  QCString blockId;
5178  if (t==DocInclude::Snippet || t==DocInclude::SnipWithLines || t==DocInclude::SnippetDoc)
5179  {
5180  if (fileName == "this") fileName=g_fileName;
5181  doctokenizerYYsetStateSnippet();
5182  tok=doctokenizerYYlex();
5183  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
5184  if (tok!=TK_WORD)
5185  {
5186  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"expected block identifier, but found token %s instead while parsing the %s command",
5187  tokToString(tok),qPrint(cmdName));
5188  return;
5189  }
5190  blockId = "["+g_token->name+"]";
5191  }
5192 
5193  // This is the only place to handle the \includedoc and \snippetdoc commands,
5194  // as the content is included here as if it is really here.
5195  if (t==DocInclude::IncludeDoc || t==DocInclude::SnippetDoc)
5196  {
5197  QCString inc_text;
5198  int inc_line = 1;
5199  readTextFileByName(fileName,inc_text);
5200  if (t==DocInclude::SnippetDoc)
5201  {
5202  inc_line = lineBlock(inc_text, blockId);
5203  inc_text = extractBlock(inc_text, blockId);
5204  }
5205  docParserPushContext();
5206  g_fileName = fileName;
5207  doctokenizerYYlineno=inc_line;
5208  internalValidatingParseDoc(this,m_children,inc_text);
5209  docParserPopContext();
5210  }
5211  else
5212  {
5213  DocInclude *inc = new DocInclude(this,fileName,g_context,t,g_isExample,g_exampleName,blockId);
5214  m_children.append(inc);
5215  inc->parse();
5216  }
5217 }

5264 
5265 int DocPara::handleStartCode()
5266 {
5267  int retval = doctokenizerYYlex();
5268  QCString lang = g_token->name;
5269  if (!lang.isEmpty() && lang.at(0)!='.')
5270  {
5271  lang="."+lang;
5272  }
5273  if (g_xmlComment)
5274  {
5275  g_token->verb = substitute(substitute(g_token->verb,"&lt;","<"),"&gt;",">");
5276  }
5277  // search for the first non-whitespace line, index is stored in li
5278  int i=0,li=0,l=g_token->verb.length();
5279  while (i<l && (g_token->verb.at(i)==' ' || g_token->verb.at(i)=='\n'))
5280  {
5281  if (g_token->verb.at(i)=='\n') li=i+1;
5282  i++;
5283  }
5284  m_children.append(new DocVerbatim(this,g_context,stripIndentation(g_token->verb.mid(li)),DocVerbatim::Code,g_isExample,g_exampleName,FALSE,lang));
5285  if (retval==0) warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"code section ended without end marker");
5286  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
5287  return retval;
5288 }
5289 
5290 void DocPara::handleInheritDoc()
5291 {
5292  if (g_memberDef) // inheriting docs from a member
5293  {
5294  MemberDef *reMd = g_memberDef->reimplements();
5295  if (reMd) // member from which was inherited.
5296  {
5297  MemberDef *thisMd = g_memberDef;
5298  //printf("{InheritDocs:%s=>%s}\n",g_memberDef->qualifiedName().data(),reMd->qualifiedName().data());
5299  docParserPushContext();
5300  g_scope=reMd->getOuterScope();
5301  if (g_scope!=Doxygen::globalScope)
5302  {
5303  g_context=g_scope->name();
5304  }
5305  g_memberDef=reMd;
5306  g_styleStack.clear();
5307  g_nodeStack.clear();
5308  g_copyStack.append(reMd);
5309  internalValidatingParseDoc(this,m_children,reMd->briefDescription());
5310  internalValidatingParseDoc(this,m_children,reMd->documentation());
5311  g_copyStack.remove(reMd);
5312  docParserPopContext(TRUE);
5313  g_memberDef = thisMd;
5314  }
5315  }
5316 }

5318 
5319 int DocPara::handleCommand(const QCString &cmdName)
5320 {
5321  DBG(("handleCommand(%s)\n",qPrint(cmdName)));
5322  int retval = RetVal_OK;
5323  int cmdId = Mappers::cmdMapper->map(cmdName);
5324  switch (cmdId)
5325  {
5326  case CMD_UNKNOWN:
5327  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Found unknown command `\\%s'",qPrint(cmdName));
5328  break;
5329  case CMD_EMPHASIS:
5330  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Italic,TRUE));
5331  retval=handleStyleArgument(this,m_children,cmdName);
5332  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Italic,FALSE));
5333  if (retval!=TK_WORD) m_children.append(new DocWhiteSpace(this," "));
5334  break;
5335  case CMD_BOLD:
5336  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Bold,TRUE));
5337  retval=handleStyleArgument(this,m_children,cmdName);
5338  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Bold,FALSE));
5339  if (retval!=TK_WORD) m_children.append(new DocWhiteSpace(this," "));
5340  break;
5341  case CMD_CODE:
5342  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Code,TRUE));
5343  retval=handleStyleArgument(this,m_children,cmdName);
5344  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Code,FALSE));
5345  if (retval!=TK_WORD) m_children.append(new DocWhiteSpace(this," "));
5346  break;
5347  case CMD_BSLASH:
5348  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_BSlash));
5349  break;
5350  case CMD_AT:
5351  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_At));
5352  break;
5353  case CMD_LESS:
5354  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Less));
5355  break;
5356  case CMD_GREATER:
5357  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Greater));
5358  break;
5359  case CMD_AMP:
5360  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Amp));
5361  break;
5362  case CMD_DOLLAR:
5363  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Dollar));
5364  break;
5365  case CMD_HASH:
5366  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Hash));
5367  break;
5368  case CMD_PIPE:
5369  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Pipe));
5370  break;
5371  case CMD_DCOLON:
5372  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_DoubleColon));
5373  break;
5374  case CMD_PERCENT:
5375  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Percent));
5376  break;
5377  case CMD_NDASH:
5378  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Minus));
5379  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Minus));
5380  break;
5381  case CMD_MDASH:
5382  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Minus));
5383  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Minus));
5384  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Minus));
5385  break;
5386  case CMD_QUOTE:
5387  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Quot));
5388  break;
5389  case CMD_PUNT:
5390  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Dot));
5391  break;
5392  case CMD_PLUS:
5393  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Plus));
5394  break;
5395  case CMD_MINUS:
5396  m_children.append(new DocSymbol(this,DocSymbol::Sym_Minus));
5397  break;
5398  case CMD_SA:
5399  g_inSeeBlock=TRUE;
5400  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::See);
5401  g_inSeeBlock=FALSE;
5402  break;
5403  case CMD_RETURN:
5404  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Return);
5405  g_hasReturnCommand=TRUE;
5406  break;
5407  case CMD_AUTHOR:
5408  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Author);
5409  break;
5410  case CMD_AUTHORS:
5411  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Authors);
5412  break;
5413  case CMD_VERSION:
5414  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Version);
5415  break;
5416  case CMD_SINCE:
5417  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Since);
5418  break;
5419  case CMD_DATE:
5420  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Date);
5421  break;
5422  case CMD_NOTE:
5423  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Note);
5424  break;
5425  case CMD_WARNING:
5426  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Warning);
5427  break;
5428  case CMD_PRE:
5429  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Pre);
5430  break;
5431  case CMD_POST:
5432  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Post);
5433  break;
5434  case CMD_COPYRIGHT:
5435  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Copyright);
5436  break;
5437  case CMD_INVARIANT:
5438  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Invar);
5439  break;
5440  case CMD_REMARK:
5441  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Remark);
5442  break;

5448  break;

5571  doctokenizerYYsetStateMsc();

5573  dv->setText(g_token->verb);
5574  dv->setWidth(width);
5575  dv->setHeight(height);
5576  m_children.append(dv);
5577  if (retval==0) warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"msc section ended without end marker");
5578  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
5579  }
5580  break;
5581  case CMD_STARTUML:
5582  {

5584  doctokenizerYYsetStatePlantUMLOpt();

5586  QCString plantFile(g_token->sectionId);
5587  DocVerbatim *dv = new DocVerbatim(this,g_context,g_token->verb,DocVerbatim::PlantUML,FALSE,plantFile);

5604  }
5605  if (retval==0) warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"startuml section ended without end marker");
5606  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
5607  }
5608  break;
5609  case CMD_ENDPARBLOCK:
5610  retval=RetVal_EndParBlock;
5611  break;
5612  case CMD_ENDCODE:
5613  case CMD_ENDHTMLONLY:
5614  case CMD_ENDMANONLY:
5615  case CMD_ENDRTFONLY:
5616  case CMD_ENDLATEXONLY:
5617  case CMD_ENDXMLONLY:
5618  case CMD_ENDDBONLY:
5619  case CMD_ENDLINK:
5620  case CMD_ENDVERBATIM:
5621  case CMD_ENDDOT:
5622  case CMD_ENDMSC:
5623  case CMD_ENDUML:
5624  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected command %s",qPrint(g_token->name));
5625  break;
5626  case CMD_PARAM:
5627  retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::Param,FALSE,g_token->paramDir);
5628  break;
5629  case CMD_TPARAM:
5630  retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::TemplateParam,FALSE,g_token->paramDir);
5631  break;
5632  case CMD_RETVAL:
5633  retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::RetVal);
5634  break;
5635  case CMD_EXCEPTION:
5636  retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::Exception);
5637  break;

5639  retval = handleXRefItem();
5640  break;
5641  case CMD_LINEBREAK:
5642  {
5643  DocLineBreak *lb = new DocLineBreak(this);
5644  m_children.append(lb);
5645  }
5646  break;
5647  case CMD_ANCHOR:
5648  {
5649  DocAnchor *anchor = handleAnchor(this);
5650  if (anchor)
5651  {
5652  m_children.append(anchor);
5653  }
5654  }
5655  break;
5656  case CMD_ADDINDEX:
5657  {
5658  DocIndexEntry *ie = new DocIndexEntry(this,
5659  g_scope!=Doxygen::globalScope?g_scope:0,
5660  g_memberDef);
5661  m_children.append(ie);
5662  retval = ie->parse();
5663  }
5664  break;
5665  case CMD_INTERNAL:
5666  retval = RetVal_Internal;
5667  break;
5668  case CMD_ENDINTERNAL:
5669  retval = RetVal_EndInternal;
5670  break;
5671  case CMD_PARBLOCK:
5672  {
5673  DocParBlock *block = new DocParBlock(this);
5674  m_children.append(block);
5675  retval = block->parse();
5676  }
5677  break;
5678  case CMD_COPYDOC: // fall through
5679  case CMD_COPYBRIEF: // fall through
5680  case CMD_COPYDETAILS:
5681  //retval = RetVal_CopyDoc;
5682  // these commands should already be resolved by processCopyDoc()
5683  break;
5684  case CMD_INCLUDE:
5685  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::Include);
5686  break;
5687  case CMD_INCWITHLINES:
5688  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::IncWithLines);
5689  break;
5690  case CMD_DONTINCLUDE:
5691  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::DontInclude);
5692  break;
5693  case CMD_HTMLINCLUDE:
5694  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::HtmlInclude);
5695  break;

5697  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::LatexInclude);
5698  break;

5701  break;

5703  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::Snippet);
5704  break;
5705  case CMD_SNIPWITHLINES:
5706  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::SnipWithLines);
5707  break;
5708  case CMD_INCLUDEDOC:
5709  handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::IncludeDoc);
5710  break;
5711  case CMD_SNIPPETDOC:

5713  break;

5716  break;

5719  break;

5722  break;

5725  break;

5728  break;

5731  break;

5734  break;
5735  case CMD_MSCFILE:
5736  handleFile<DocMscFile>(cmdName);
5737  break;
5738  case CMD_DIAFILE:
5739  handleFile<DocDiaFile>(cmdName);
5740  break;

5750  case CMD_REF: // fall through
5751  case CMD_SUBPAGE:
5752  handleRef(cmdName);
5753  break;
5754  case CMD_SECREFLIST:
5755  {
5756  DocSecRefList *list = new DocSecRefList(this);
5757  m_children.append(list);
5758  list->parse();
5759  }
5760  break;
5761  case CMD_SECREFITEM:
5762  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected command %s",qPrint(g_token->name));
5763  break;
5764  case CMD_ENDSECREFLIST:
5765  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected command %s",qPrint(g_token->name));
5766  break;
5767  case CMD_FORMULA:
5768  {
5769  DocFormula *form=new DocFormula(this,g_token->id);
5770  m_children.append(form);
5771  }
5772  break;
5773  //case CMD_LANGSWITCH:
5774  // retval = handleLanguageSwitch();
5775  // break;
5776  case CMD_INTERNALREF:
5777  //warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"unexpected command %s",qPrint(g_token->name));
5778  {
5779  DocInternalRef *ref = handleInternalRef(this);
5780  if (ref)
5781  {
5782  m_children.append(ref);
5783  ref->parse();
5784  }
5785  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
5786  }
5787  break;
5788  case CMD_INHERITDOC:
5789  handleInheritDoc();
5790  break;
5791  default:
5792  // we should not get here!
5793  ASSERT(0);
5794  break;
5795  }
5796  INTERNAL_ASSERT(retval==0 || retval==RetVal_OK || retval==RetVal_SimpleSec ||
5797  retval==TK_LISTITEM || retval==TK_ENDLIST || retval==TK_NEWPARA ||
5798  retval==RetVal_Section || retval==RetVal_EndList ||
5799  retval==RetVal_Internal || retval==RetVal_SwitchLang ||
5800  retval==RetVal_EndInternal
5801  );
5802  DBG(("handleCommand(%s) end retval=%x\n",qPrint(cmdName),retval));
5803  return retval;
5804 }
5805 
5806 static bool findAttribute(const HtmlAttribList &tagHtmlAttribs,
5807  const char *attrName,
5808  QCString *result)
5809 {
5810 
5811  HtmlAttribListIterator li(tagHtmlAttribs);
5812  HtmlAttrib *opt;
5813  for (li.toFirst();(opt=li.current());++li)
5814  {
5815  if (opt->name==attrName)
5816  {
5817  *result = opt->value;
5818  return TRUE;
5819  }
5820  }
5821  return FALSE;
5822 }
5823 
5824 int DocPara::handleHtmlStartTag(const QCString &tagName,const HtmlAttribList &tagHtmlAttribs)
5825 {
5826  DBG(("handleHtmlStartTag(%s,%d)\n",qPrint(tagName),tagHtmlAttribs.count()));
5827  int retval=RetVal_OK;
5828  int tagId = Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(tagName);
5829  if (g_token->emptyTag && !(tagId&XML_CmdMask) &&
5830  tagId!=HTML_UNKNOWN && tagId!=HTML_IMG && tagId!=HTML_BR)
5831  {
5832  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"HTML tags may not use the 'empty tag' XHTML syntax.");
5833  }
5834  switch (tagId)
5835  {
5836  case HTML_UL:
5837  {
5838  DocHtmlList *list = new DocHtmlList(this,tagHtmlAttribs,DocHtmlList::Unordered);
5839  m_children.append(list);
5840  retval=list->parse();
5841  }
5842  break;
5843  case HTML_OL:
5844  {
5845  DocHtmlList *list = new DocHtmlList(this,tagHtmlAttribs,DocHtmlList::Ordered);
5846  m_children.append(list);
5847  retval=list->parse();
5848  }
5849  break;
5850  case HTML_LI:
5851  if (!insideUL(this) && !insideOL(this))
5852  {
5853  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"lonely <li> tag found");
5854  }
5855  else
5856  {
5857  retval=RetVal_ListItem;
5858  }
5859  break;
5860  case HTML_BOLD:
5861  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Bold,&g_token->attribs);
5862  break;
5863  case HTML_CODE:
5864  if (/*getLanguageFromFileName(g_fileName)==SrcLangExt_CSharp ||*/ g_xmlComment)
5865  // for C# source or inside a <summary> or <remark> section we
5866  // treat <code> as an XML tag (so similar to @code)
5867  {
5868  doctokenizerYYsetStateXmlCode();
5869  retval = handleStartCode();
5870  }
5871  else // normal HTML markup
5872  {
5873  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Code,&g_token->attribs);
5874  }
5875  break;
5876  case HTML_EMPHASIS:
5877  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Italic,&g_token->attribs);
5878  break;
5879  case HTML_DIV:
5880  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Div,&g_token->attribs);
5881  break;
5882  case HTML_SPAN:
5883  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Span,&g_token->attribs);
5884  break;
5885  case HTML_SUB:
5886  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Subscript,&g_token->attribs);
5887  break;
5888  case HTML_SUP:
5889  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Superscript,&g_token->attribs);
5890  break;
5891  case HTML_CENTER:
5892  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Center,&g_token->attribs);
5893  break;
5894  case HTML_SMALL:
5895  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Small,&g_token->attribs);
5896  break;
5897  case HTML_PRE:
5898  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Preformatted,&g_token->attribs);
5899  setInsidePreformatted(TRUE);
5900  doctokenizerYYsetInsidePre(TRUE);
5901  break;
5902  case HTML_P:
5903  retval=TK_NEWPARA;
5904  break;
5905  case HTML_DL:
5906  {
5907  DocHtmlDescList *list = new DocHtmlDescList(this,tagHtmlAttribs);
5908  m_children.append(list);
5909  retval=list->parse();
5910  }
5911  break;
5912  case HTML_DT:
5913  retval = RetVal_DescTitle;
5914  break;
5915  case HTML_DD:
5916  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag <dd> found");
5917  break;
5918  case HTML_TABLE:
5919  {
5920  DocHtmlTable *table = new DocHtmlTable(this,tagHtmlAttribs);
5921  m_children.append(table);
5922  retval=table->parse();
5923  }
5924  break;
5925  case HTML_TR:
5926  retval = RetVal_TableRow;
5927  break;
5928  case HTML_TD:
5929  retval = RetVal_TableCell;
5930  break;
5931  case HTML_TH:
5932  retval = RetVal_TableHCell;
5933  break;
5934  case HTML_CAPTION:
5935  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag <caption> found");
5936  break;
5937  case HTML_BR:
5938  {
5939  DocLineBreak *lb = new DocLineBreak(this);
5940  m_children.append(lb);
5941  }
5942  break;
5943  case HTML_HR:
5944  {
5945  DocHorRuler *hr = new DocHorRuler(this);
5946  m_children.append(hr);
5947  }
5948  break;
5949  case HTML_A:
5950  retval=handleAHref(this,m_children,tagHtmlAttribs);
5951  break;
5952  case HTML_H1:
5953  retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,1);
5954  break;
5955  case HTML_H2:
5956  retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,2);
5957  break;
5958  case HTML_H3:
5959  retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,3);
5960  break;
5961  case HTML_H4:
5962  retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,4);
5963  break;
5964  case HTML_H5:
5965  retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,5);
5966  break;
5967  case HTML_H6:
5968  retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,6);
5969  break;
5970  case HTML_IMG:
5971  {
5972  handleImg(this,m_children,tagHtmlAttribs);
5973  }
5974  break;
5975  case HTML_BLOCKQUOTE:
5976  {
5977  DocHtmlBlockQuote *block = new DocHtmlBlockQuote(this,tagHtmlAttribs);
5978  m_children.append(block);
5979  retval = block->parse();
5980  }
5981  break;
5982 
5983  case XML_SUMMARY:
5984  case XML_REMARKS:
5985  case XML_EXAMPLE:
5986  g_xmlComment=TRUE;
5987  // fall through
5988  case XML_VALUE:
5989  case XML_PARA:
5990  if (!m_children.isEmpty())
5991  {
5992  retval = TK_NEWPARA;
5993  }
5994  break;
5995  case XML_DESCRIPTION:
5996  if (insideTable(this))
5997  {
5998  retval=RetVal_TableCell;
5999  }
6000  break;
6001  case XML_C:
6002  handleStyleEnter(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Code,&g_token->attribs);
6003  break;
6004  case XML_PARAM:
6005  case XML_TYPEPARAM:
6006  {
6007  g_xmlComment=TRUE;
6008  QCString paramName;
6009  if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"name",&paramName))
6010  {
6011  if (paramName.isEmpty())
6012  {
6013  if (Config_getBool(WARN_NO_PARAMDOC))
6014  {
6015  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"empty 'name' attribute for <param%s> tag.",tagId==XML_PARAM?"":"type");
6016  }
6017  }
6018  else
6019  {
6020  retval = handleParamSection(paramName,
6021  tagId==XML_PARAM ? DocParamSect::Param : DocParamSect::TemplateParam,
6022  TRUE);
6023  }
6024  }
6025  else
6026  {
6027  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Missing 'name' attribute from <param%s> tag.",tagId==XML_PARAM?"":"type");
6028  }
6029  }
6030  break;
6031  case XML_PARAMREF:
6032  case XML_TYPEPARAMREF:
6033  {
6034  QCString paramName;
6035  if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"name",&paramName))
6036  {
6037  //printf("paramName=%s\n",paramName.data());
6038  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Italic,TRUE));
6039  m_children.append(new DocWord(this,paramName));
6040  m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Italic,FALSE));
6041  if (retval!=TK_WORD) m_children.append(new DocWhiteSpace(this," "));
6042  }
6043  else
6044  {
6045  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Missing 'name' attribute from <param%sref> tag.",tagId==XML_PARAMREF?"":"type");
6046  }
6047  }
6048  break;
6049  case XML_EXCEPTION:
6050  {
6051  g_xmlComment=TRUE;
6052  QCString exceptName;
6053  if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"cref",&exceptName))
6054  {
6055  unescapeCRef(exceptName);
6056  retval = handleParamSection(exceptName,DocParamSect::Exception,TRUE);
6057  }
6058  else
6059  {
6060  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Missing 'cref' attribute from <exception> tag.");
6061  }
6062  }
6063  break;
6064  case XML_ITEM:
6065  case XML_LISTHEADER:
6066  if (insideTable(this))
6067  {
6068  retval=RetVal_TableRow;
6069  }
6070  else if (insideUL(this) || insideOL(this))
6071  {
6072  retval=RetVal_ListItem;
6073  }
6074  else
6075  {
6076  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"lonely <item> tag found");
6077  }
6078  break;
6079  case XML_RETURNS:
6080  g_xmlComment=TRUE;
6081  retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Return,TRUE);
6082  g_hasReturnCommand=TRUE;
6083  break;
6084  case XML_TERM:
6085  //m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Bold,TRUE));
6086  if (insideTable(this))
6087  {
6088  retval=RetVal_TableCell;
6089  }
6090  break;
6091  case XML_SEE:
6092  // I'm not sure if <see> is the same as <seealso> or if it
6093  // should you link a member without producing a section. The
6094  // C# specification is extremely vague about this (but what else
6095  // can we expect from Microsoft...)
6096  {
6097  QCString cref;
6098  //printf("XML_SEE: empty tag=%d\n",g_token->emptyTag);
6099  if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"cref",&cref))
6100  {
6101  unescapeCRef(cref);
6102  if (g_token->emptyTag) // <see cref="..."/> style
6103  {
6104  bool inSeeBlock = g_inSeeBlock;
6105  g_token->name = cref;
6106  g_inSeeBlock = TRUE;
6107  handleLinkedWord(this,m_children,TRUE);
6108  g_inSeeBlock = inSeeBlock;
6109  }
6110  else // <see cref="...">...</see> style
6111  {
6112  //DocRef *ref = new DocRef(this,cref);
6113  //m_children.append(ref);
6114  //ref->parse();
6115  doctokenizerYYsetStatePara();
6116  DocLink *lnk = new DocLink(this,cref);
6117  m_children.append(lnk);
6118  QCString leftOver = lnk->parse(FALSE,TRUE);
6119  if (!leftOver.isEmpty())
6120  {
6121  m_children.append(new DocWord(this,leftOver));
6122  }
6123  }
6124  }
6125  else
6126  {
6127  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Missing 'cref' attribute from <see> tag.");
6128  }
6129  }
6130  break;
6131  case XML_SEEALSO:
6132  {
6133  g_xmlComment=TRUE;
6134  QCString cref;
6135  if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"cref",&cref))
6136  {
6137  unescapeCRef(cref);
6138  // Look for an existing "see" section
6139  DocSimpleSect *ss=0;
6140  QListIterator<DocNode> cli(m_children);
6141  DocNode *n;
6142  for (cli.toFirst();(n=cli.current());++cli)
6143  {
6144  if (n->kind()==Kind_SimpleSect && ((DocSimpleSect *)n)->type()==DocSimpleSect::See)
6145  {
6146  ss = (DocSimpleSect *)n;
6147  }
6148  }
6149 
6150  if (!ss) // start new section
6151  {
6152  ss=new DocSimpleSect(this,DocSimpleSect::See);
6153  m_children.append(ss);
6154  }
6155 
6156  ss->appendLinkWord(cref);
6157  retval = RetVal_OK;
6158  }
6159  else
6160  {
6161  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Missing 'cref' attribute from <seealso> tag.");
6162  }
6163  }
6164  break;
6165  case XML_LIST:
6166  {
6167  QCString type;
6168  findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"type",&type);
6169  DocHtmlList::Type listType = DocHtmlList::Unordered;
6170  HtmlAttribList emptyList;
6171  if (type=="number")
6172  {
6173  listType=DocHtmlList::Ordered;
6174  }
6175  if (type=="table")
6176  {
6177  DocHtmlTable *table = new DocHtmlTable(this,emptyList);
6178  m_children.append(table);
6179  retval=table->parseXml();
6180  }
6181  else
6182  {
6183  DocHtmlList *list = new DocHtmlList(this,emptyList,listType);
6184  m_children.append(list);
6185  retval=list->parseXml();
6186  }
6187  }
6188  break;
6189  case XML_INCLUDE:
6190  case XML_PERMISSION:
6191  // These tags are defined in .Net but are currently unsupported
6192  g_xmlComment=TRUE;
6193  break;
6194  case HTML_UNKNOWN:
6195  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unsupported xml/html tag <%s> found", qPrint(tagName));
6196  m_children.append(new DocWord(this, "<"+tagName+tagHtmlAttribs.toString()+">"));
6197  break;
6198  case XML_INHERITDOC:
6199  handleInheritDoc();
6200  break;
6201  default:
6202  // we should not get here!
6203  ASSERT(0);
6204  break;
6205  }
6206  return retval;
6207 }

6209 int DocPara::handleHtmlEndTag(const QCString &tagName)
6210 {
6211  DBG(("handleHtmlEndTag(%s)\n",qPrint(tagName)));
6212  int tagId = Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(tagName);
6213  int retval=RetVal_OK;
6214  switch (tagId)
6215  {
6216  case HTML_UL:
6217  if (!insideUL(this))
6218  {
6219  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"found </ul> tag without matching <ul>");
6220  }
6221  else
6222  {
6223  retval=RetVal_EndList;
6224  }
6225  break;
6226  case HTML_OL:
6227  if (!insideOL(this))
6228  {
6229  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"found </ol> tag without matching <ol>");
6230  }
6231  else
6232  {
6233  retval=RetVal_EndList;
6234  }
6235  break;
6236  case HTML_LI:
6237  if (!insideLI(this))
6238  {
6239  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"found </li> tag without matching <li>");
6240  }
6241  else
6242  {
6243  // ignore </li> tags
6244  }
6245  break;
6246  case HTML_BLOCKQUOTE:
6247  retval=RetVal_EndBlockQuote;
6248  break;
6249  //case HTML_PRE:
6250  // if (!insidePRE(this))
6251  // {
6252  // warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"found </pre> tag without matching <pre>");
6253  // }
6254  // else
6255  // {
6256  // retval=RetVal_EndPre;
6257  // }
6258  // break;
6259  case HTML_BOLD:
6260  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Bold,"b");
6261  break;
6262  case HTML_CODE:
6263  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Code,"code");
6264  break;
6265  case HTML_EMPHASIS:
6266  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Italic,"em");
6267  break;
6268  case HTML_DIV:
6269  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Div,"div");
6270  break;
6271  case HTML_SPAN:
6272  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Span,"span");
6273  break;
6274  case HTML_SUB:
6275  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Subscript,"sub");
6276  break;
6277  case HTML_SUP:
6278  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Superscript,"sup");
6279  break;
6280  case HTML_CENTER:
6281  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Center,"center");
6282  break;
6283  case HTML_SMALL:
6284  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Small,"small");
6285  break;
6286  case HTML_PRE:
6287  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Preformatted,"pre");
6288  setInsidePreformatted(FALSE);
6289  doctokenizerYYsetInsidePre(FALSE);
6290  break;
6291  case HTML_P:
6292  retval=TK_NEWPARA;
6293  break;
6294  case HTML_DL:
6295  retval=RetVal_EndDesc;
6296  break;
6297  case HTML_DT:
6298  // ignore </dt> tag
6299  break;
6300  case HTML_DD:
6301  // ignore </dd> tag
6302  break;
6303  case HTML_TABLE:
6304  retval=RetVal_EndTable;
6305  break;
6306  case HTML_TR:
6307  // ignore </tr> tag
6308  break;
6309  case HTML_TD:
6310  // ignore </td> tag
6311  break;
6312  case HTML_TH:
6313  // ignore </th> tag
6314  break;
6315  case HTML_CAPTION:
6316  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </caption> found");
6317  break;
6318  case HTML_BR:
6319  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Illegal </br> tag found\n");
6320  break;
6321  case HTML_H1:
6322  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </h1> found");
6323  break;
6324  case HTML_H2:
6325  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </h2> found");
6326  break;
6327  case HTML_H3:
6328  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </h3> found");
6329  break;
6330  case HTML_H4:
6331  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </h4> found");
6332  break;
6333  case HTML_H5:
6334  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </h5> found");
6335  break;
6336  case HTML_H6:
6337  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </h6> found");
6338  break;
6339  case HTML_IMG:
6340  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </img> found");
6341  break;
6342  case HTML_HR:
6343  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </hr> found");
6344  break;
6345  case HTML_A:
6346  //warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected tag </a> found");
6347  // ignore </a> tag (can be part of <a name=...></a>
6348  break;
6349 
6350  case XML_TERM:
6351  //m_children.append(new DocStyleChange(this,g_nodeStack.count(),DocStyleChange::Bold,FALSE));
6352  break;
6353  case XML_SUMMARY:
6354  case XML_REMARKS:
6355  case XML_PARA:
6356  case XML_VALUE:
6357  case XML_EXAMPLE:
6358  case XML_PARAM:
6359  case XML_LIST:
6360  case XML_TYPEPARAM:
6361  case XML_RETURNS:
6362  case XML_SEE:
6363  case XML_SEEALSO:
6364  case XML_EXCEPTION:
6365  case XML_INHERITDOC:
6366  retval = RetVal_CloseXml;
6367  break;
6368  case XML_C:
6369  handleStyleLeave(this,m_children,DocStyleChange::Code,"c");
6370  break;
6371  case XML_ITEM:
6372  case XML_LISTHEADER:
6373  case XML_INCLUDE:

6382  m_children.append(new DocWord(this,"</"+tagName+">"));
6383  break;
6384  default:
6385  // we should not get here!
6386  warn_doc_error(g_fileName,doctokenizerYYlineno,"Unexpected end tag %s\n",qPrint(tagName));
6387  ASSERT(0);
6388  break;
